captions.text:
Hey everybody thanks for watching.
Be sure to check out the vocal version of

this tune right over here. We collaborated
with none other than Megan Nicole and Alex

Goot they were awesome to work with, love
them, go subscribe. We have sheet music coming

everybody. We got lots of requests for 1000
Years, this tune, it's all coming, go to our

website. And be sure to snag our album if
you haven't already. The link is in the description
below. See you on the next tune.
